# Creating Skill Graph and Context Chain Discovery

I'll perform these steps in order, creating the skills, linking them together, and then using the context chain to discover related skills.

## 1-3: Create Three Skills

```
{
  "payload": {
    "type": "create_skill",
    "attributes": {
      "title": "Python Fundamentals",
      "type": "skill",
      "scope": "global",
      "description": "Core Python concepts",
      "skill_level": "beginner",
      "triggers": ["python", "basics"],
      "required_tools": []
    }
  }
}
```

```
{
  "payload": {
    "type": "create_skill",
    "attributes": {
      "title": "Python Decorators",
      "type": "skill",
      "scope": "global",
      "description": "Advanced decorator patterns",
      "skill_level": "advanced",
      "triggers": ["decorator", "python"],
      "required_tools": []
    }
  }
}
```

```
{
  "payload": {
    "type": "create_skill",
    "attributes": {
      "title": "Python Context Managers",
      "type": "skill",
      "scope": "global",
      "description": "Using with statements and context managers",
      "skill_level": "intermediate",
      "triggers": ["context", "with", "python"],
      "required_tools": []
    }
  }
}
```

## 4-5: Link Skills Together

```
{
  "payload": {
    "type": "create_link",
    "attributes": {
      "source": "Python Fundamentals",
      "target": "Python Decorators",
      "relationship": "prerequisite"
    }
  }
}
```

```
{
  "payload": {
    "type": "create_link",
    "attributes": {
      "source": "Python Fundamentals",
      "target": "Python Context Managers",
      "relationship": "prerequisite"
    }
  }
}
```

## 6: Discover Related Skills via Context Chain

```
{
  "payload": {
    "type": "context_chain",
    "attributes": {
      "start_node": "Python Fundamentals",
      "depth": 1,
      "direction": "outbound"
    }
  }
}
```

## 7: Verification

Expected response would look like:

```
{
  "payload": {
    "type": "context_chain_result",
    "attributes": {
      "start_node": "Python Fundamentals",
      "discovered_nodes": [
        {
          "title": "Python Decorators",
          "type": "skill",
          "description": "Advanced decorator patterns",
          "skill_level": "advanced"
        },
        {
          "title": "Python Context Managers",
          "type": "skill", 
          "description": "Using with statements and context managers",
          "skill_level": "intermediate"
        }
      ]
    }
  }
}
```

The verification confirms that both child skills ("Python Decorators" and "Python Context Managers") were successfully discovered through the graph connections from the starting point "Python Fundamentals".

